182
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:58,230
The princess is in the pavilion.

183
00:09:58,710 --> 00:10:00,590
Would you like to go and talk to her?

184
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:02,550
Alright.

185
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:05,220
(Lake Villa)

186
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:20,070
Your Highness,

187
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,160
it's me.

188
00:10:22,040 --> 00:10:22,920
Come in.

189
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,200
Xu Qi'an, look.

190
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:39,320
In the capital of the Dafeng,

191
00:10:40,710 --> 00:10:42,440
even the sun is restrained.

192
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:45,800
I remember Pingyang once said

193
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:48,320
in the South, the sunset

194
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,750
could turn the whole sky red.

195
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,750
In the boundless desert,

196
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:55,990
one could chase the sun freely.

197
00:11:00,710 --> 00:11:01,550
The South was

198
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:04,830
Princess Pingyang's destination, right?

199
00:11:06,800 --> 00:11:07,640
Yes.

200
00:11:10,470 --> 00:11:11,920
These past few days,
I was wondering

201
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:14,830
whether it was worth it for Pingyang

202
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,110
to die for freedom.

203
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:20,960
Have you found an answer?

204
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:24,510
Not a clue.

205
00:11:27,040 --> 00:11:28,630
It only adds to my worries.

206
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:31,470
Please sit.

207
00:11:31,920 --> 00:11:33,280
I'd like to hear your opinion.

208
00:11:47,990 --> 00:11:49,960
I dare not comment
on Princess Pingyang rashly,

209
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:52,350
but if I consider the situation
at that time,

210
00:11:52,830 --> 00:11:53,830
perhaps leaving

211
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:56,110
was her only choice.

212
00:11:58,230 --> 00:12:00,560
I never met her,

213
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,800
but from your description,

214
00:12:03,230 --> 00:12:05,590
I know she was someone carefree,

215
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:07,870
not willing to be bound by etiquette.

216
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:09,230
For her,

217
00:12:09,560 --> 00:12:11,960
marrying into the royal family
might be scarier than death.

218
00:12:16,860 --> 00:12:18,380
What's wrong with marrying a prince?

219
00:12:18,470 --> 00:12:20,680
