luxurious, and noble life.

220
00:12:21,440 --> 00:12:24,160
This is what many ladies dream of.

221
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,680
Then they can go and be one.

222
00:12:26,400 --> 00:12:27,710
Anyway, I don't want to.

223
00:12:29,230 --> 00:12:30,070
Listen.

224
00:12:30,350 --> 00:12:32,080
Compared with marrying
a man without love

225
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,630
and being trapped in a life of pretense,

226
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,280
I'd rather die.

227
00:12:39,200 --> 00:12:42,230
I'll help you escape the Palace.

228
00:12:42,750 --> 00:12:43,750
You're flying!

229
00:12:46,160 --> 00:12:47,470
- Higher!
- You're flying!

230
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:00,800
I misspoke.

231
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,750
Please forgive me.

232
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,440
You're right.

233
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:12,470
That was Pingyang's only choice.

234
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,590
It's also mine now.

235
00:13:21,350 --> 00:13:22,710
My mother once told me

236
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,780
that to marry into the noble families,

237
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:25,920
to stabilize the court,

238
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:28,300
and to ease my father's worries,

239
00:13:28,470 --> 00:13:29,800
is the destiny of a princess.

240
00:13:31,590 --> 00:13:33,200
I'm not far from that day.

241
00:13:34,990 --> 00:13:35,830
Your Highness.

242
00:13:36,350 --> 00:13:37,280
Now that you're here,

243
00:13:37,470 --> 00:13:38,630
have a drink with me.

244
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:41,110
Your wish is my command.

245
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,630
There will be fireworks later.

246
00:14:05,560 --> 00:14:06,400
Your Highness,

247
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:09,080
your fireworks are different
from the ones I've seen.

248
00:14:09,440 --> 00:14:10,400
They're quite beautiful.

249
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:27,710
Xu Qi'an,

250
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,750
do you think Princess Pingyang
might not have died,

251
00:14:33,400 --> 00:14:34,920
but instead went to another world,

252
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,510
watching fireworks with us?

253
00:14:39,350 --> 00:14:40,190
Yes.

254
00:14:41,230 --> 00:14:42,310
In that world,

255
00:14:42,310 --> 00:14:44,370
there is no concept of ruler and subject

256
00:14:44,750 --> 00:14:45,590
and of high and low.

257
00:14:45,830 --> 00:14:47,400
Everyone is born equal.

258
00:14:47,510 --> 00:14:49,320
There's no such thing
as parental commands

259
00:14:49,590 --> 00:14:50,960
or arranged marriages.

260
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,990
In the sea of people,

261
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,400
if two people meet

262
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:55,870
and fall in love,

263
00:14:56,560 --> 00:14:58,030
they can walk hand in hand for life.

264
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:15,990
Even if they don't meet a good match,

265
00:15:16,510 --> 00:15:18,540
there's no need to settle
due to outside pressure.

266
00:15:19,040 --> 00:15:21,230
Living alone is just as good.

267
00:15:21,470 --> 00:15:24,870
You can go anywhere you want

268
00:15:24,870 --> 00:15:26,590
and do whatever you want to do.

269
00:15:27,510 --> 00:15:28,750
Is there really such a world?

270
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:29,640
Of course.

271
00:15:30,710 --> 00:15:32,750
Not only can women live
without marrying,

272
00:15:32,870 --> 00:15:34,110
in that world,

273
00:15:34,110 --> 00:15:35,800
women, like men,

274
00:15:35,860 --> 00:15:37,750
can go out, struggle,
and pursue their dreams,

275
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:39,110
to realize their own worth.

276
00:15:39,440 --> 00:15:42,630
When they grow old,
they can buy a house with friends

277
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:44,800
and live a simple, happy life.

278
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:03,110
If such a world exists,

279
00:16:05,200 --> 00:16:06,750
I really want to see it.

280
00:16:08,870 --> 00:16:10,080
But...

281
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:12,590
But what?

282
00:16:13,160 --> 00:16:15,800
But I'm not as beautiful as Pingyang.

283
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:18,680
I'm not as smart

284
00:16:19,510 --> 00:16:20,350
as she is.

285
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,280
I'm not as brave as she is.

286
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:29,110
I can't do anything.

287
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:38,110
On the contrary,

288
00:16:38,990 --> 00:16:41,630
Your Highness have many advantages.

289
00:16:42,710 --> 00:16:43,630
You're carefree,

290
00:16:44,230 --> 00:16:45,110
genuine,

291
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:46,870
and sincere toward others.

292
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:49,160
Even so,

293
00:16:49,750 --> 00:16:51,750
I wouldn't want to leave the people
in this world.

294
00:16:53,510 --> 00:16:54,830
I can't leave my mother,

295
00:16:56,550 --> 00:16:59,230
even though she always complains
that I'm useless.

296
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:00,710
And my brother.

297
00:17:01,230 --> 00:17:02,990
Every time Mother scolds me,

298
00:17:02,990 --> 00:17:05,320
he's always the first to protect me.

299
00:17:05,870 --> 00:17:07,040
And Father.

300
00:17:08,280 --> 00:17:09,710
Even though I'm a useless person,

301
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,710
he still favors me.

302
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:14,590
And Gang.

303
00:17:16,040 --> 00:17:16,920
And you.

304
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,990
Me too?

305
00:17:25,990 --> 00:17:27,960
Though we haven't known each other

306
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:29,160
for long,

307
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:32,230
I really admire your nature.

308
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:34,990
Sometimes you're as timid as a mouse,

309
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:36,440
but sometimes

310
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:38,130
you're bold enough to defy the heavens.

311
00:17:39,270 --> 00:17:40,360
You can write poems

312
00:17:41,030 --> 00:17:42,160
and solve cases,

313
00:17:42,840 --> 00:17:44,960
and you know many interesting things.

314
00:17:47,710 --> 00:17:48,790
You also know

315
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:51,200
that I love the egg-yolk puff
from Shop of Delicacies.

316
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:55,710
Mother says they're too greasy
and doesn't let me eat them.

317
00:17:56,270 --> 00:17:57,790
I have to sneak out of the Palace

318
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:59,990
to buy them myself every time.

319
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:03,790
How do you know?

320
00:18:08,360 --> 00:18:10,600
She'll understand after seeing it.

321
00:18:10,600 --> 00:18:12,660
(Shop of Delicacies)

322
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:18,960
Someone who secretly cares about you

323
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,360
told me.

324
00:18:20,880 --> 00:18:21,790
Impossible.

325
00:18:23,750 --> 00:18:25,310
Pingyang is dead.

326
00:18:25,990 --> 00:18:27,510
I have no friends left.

327
00:18:29,270 --> 00:18:30,470
Your Highness, you're drunk.

328
00:18:41,310 --> 00:18:42,840
Your Highness, if you don't mind,

329
00:18:44,270 --> 00:18:45,160
from now on,

330
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:47,920
I can be your friend.

331
00:19:10,360 --> 00:19:12,230
I don't want to be your friend.

332
00:19:13,150 --> 00:19:15,440
♪The sky is clear now;
the clouds are gone♪

333
00:19:15,820 --> 00:19:18,810
♪No more cold starts at night♪

334
00:19:19,810 --> 00:19:21,930
♪Quietly waiting
for the flowers to bloom♪

335
00:19:22,150 --> 00:19:26,190
♪Chasing the south wind
through a quiet garden♪

336
00:19:26,460 --> 00:19:28,880
♪Among all the worldly sights♪

337
00:19:29,180 --> 00:19:32,120
♪Only you are the hardest to find♪

338
00:19:43,470 --> 00:19:46,480
♪Thousands of words♪

339
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:48,910
♪For you, I can become Li Bai♪

340
00:19:48,910 --> 00:19:51,850
♪Thousands of thoughts as the preface♪

341
00:19:51,850 --> 00:19:54,060
♪Half a poem still depicts my feelings♪

342
00:19:54,060 --> 00:19:56,950
♪Thousands of simple words
make a poem♪

343
00:19:57,170 --> 00:19:59,580
♪To express my devotion to you♪

344
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:02,390
♪Thousands of thoughts as the preface♪

345
00:20:02,550 --> 00:20:04,740
♪Half a poem still depicts my feelings♪

346
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:07,610
♪Thousands of simple words make a poem♪

347
00:20:07,890 --> 00:20:10,450
♪To express my devotion to you♪

348
00:20:10,580 --> 00:20:12,790
♪All the scenes in this world♪

349
00:20:12,790 --> 00:20:15,380
♪Are beautiful because of you♪

350
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:18,310
♪Thousands of words♪
♪How to express my longing poetically♪

351
00:20:18,560 --> 00:20:20,900
♪For you, I can become Li Bai♪
♪I once read poems♪

352
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:23,840
♪Thousands of words♪
♪But even Li Bai couldn't portrait you♪

353
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:26,230
♪Half a poem still depicts my feelings♪
♪Took all the words♪

354
00:20:26,230 --> 00:20:29,230
♪Thousands of simple words make a poem♪
♪Love is a mysterious fate♪

355
00:20:29,230 --> 00:20:31,760
♪To express my devotion to you♪
♪Can't compare to true love♪

356
00:20:31,890 --> 00:20:34,230
♪All the scenes in this world♪
♪I'd use the rivers as ink♪

357
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:37,830
♪Are beautiful because of you♪
♪To write about my longing for you♪

358
00:20:52,010 --> 00:20:53,440
Your Highness, you're awake.

359
00:20:54,470 --> 00:20:55,310
Take it slow.

360
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:57,360
Take it slow. How do you feel?

361
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:02,400
I've been sleeping here all night?

362
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,680
Yes.

363
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:09,910
Where is Xu Qi'an?

364
00:21:10,270 --> 00:21:12,550
Xu Qi'an left before dawn.

365
00:21:13,070 --> 00:21:14,640
He stayed with you all night yesterday

366
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,720
and

367
00:21:15,920 --> 00:21:17,640
held your hand the whole time.

368
00:21:19,880 --> 00:21:20,720
He...

369
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:21,680
He...

370
00:21:21,740 --> 00:21:23,680
Did he take advantage of me
while I was asleep?

371
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:24,640
No, no.

372
00:21:24,750 --> 00:21:26,120
He was keeping you warm,

373
00:21:26,120 --> 00:21:27,640
driving away the cold.

374
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:32,440
Before he left, he specifically told me

375
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:34,960
that once you woke up,
you should drink this congee.

376
00:21:35,160 --> 00:21:37,010
It helps sober you up
and warm your stomach.

377
00:21:37,710 --> 00:21:38,550
Try it.

378
00:21:39,310 --> 00:21:40,310
He also said

379
00:21:40,310 --> 00:21:41,960
that he made it himself

380
00:21:42,120 --> 00:21:44,120
and added some special ingredients

381
00:21:44,510 --> 00:21:45,350
called

382
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:47,230
something like chicken powder.

383
00:21:54,230 --> 00:21:55,440
It's quite tasty.

384
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,240
This little brat.

385
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,750
He always has something new.

386
00:22:01,980 --> 00:22:04,620
(Act if you want it.)

387
00:22:10,510 --> 00:22:11,150
Senior Yang,

388
00:22:11,150 --> 00:22:13,510
(Guardians' Notice)
these are copied from the city gates.

389
00:22:13,510 --> 00:22:15,120
It indeed details

390
00:22:15,120 --> 00:22:16,680
the heroic actions of Yang Qianhuan

391
00:22:16,680 --> 00:22:18,640
from the Astronomical Bureau
in this case.

392
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:20,430
It says you made a great contribution.

393
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:28,840
I suppose my fame has spread
throughout the capital.

394
00:22:29,440 --> 00:22:31,990
Thanks to the Supervisor
for calling me back

395
00:22:31,990 --> 00:22:34,300
(Guardians' Notice)
to make contributions.

396
00:22:34,310 --> 00:22:35,150
My Master

397
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:37,160
truly didn't deceive me.

398
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:39,990
But

399
00:22:40,400 --> 00:22:42,030
I'll have to be more careful

400
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,750
when I go out

401
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:45,470
to avoid being recognized

402
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:48,200
and causing unnecessary trouble.

403
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:50,710
There's no need for that.

404
00:22:51,230 --> 00:22:52,070
After all,

405
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:54,400
no one is talking about this.

406
00:22:56,230 --> 00:22:57,070
Why?

407
00:22:59,270 --> 00:23:00,120
Senior Yang,

408
00:23:02,120 --> 00:23:03,070
this is the poem.

409
00:23:05,160 --> 00:23:07,310
Since it was spread from the court,

410
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:10,060
it's caused a huge stir
in the Directorate of Education

411
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,920
and Yunlu Academy.

412
00:23:12,230 --> 00:23:13,160
It's been hailed

413
00:23:13,550 --> 00:23:16,200
as the greatest satire poem ever.

414
00:23:16,360 --> 00:23:18,680
Now it's spread everywhere.

415
00:23:18,990 --> 00:23:22,550
Everyone praises Mr. Xu
as the Dafeng's conscience.

416
00:23:22,750 --> 00:23:25,600
I only wish my child
to be foolish and simple,

417
00:23:26,360 --> 00:23:27,750
without disaster or hardship,

418
00:23:28,440 --> 00:23:30,230
to become a public official.

419
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,120
Why?

420
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:34,790
Why is it that Xu Ningyan

421
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:38,600
can always do things

422
00:23:39,270 --> 00:23:41,440
that everyone envies?

423
00:23:43,750 --> 00:23:46,470
He single-handedly solved
the Sangbo Case

424
00:23:47,400 --> 00:23:48,790
and scolded the powerful

425
00:23:49,160 --> 00:23:50,920
when he was beneath everyone.

426
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:54,270
It's not fair.

427
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:56,440
It's not fair.

428
00:23:57,840 --> 00:24:00,260
It's so unfair.

429
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,520
Senior Yang,

430
00:24:02,300 --> 00:24:03,310
are you alright?

431
00:24:05,740 --> 00:24:06,640
I have

432
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:09,960
realized it.

433
00:24:11,510 --> 00:24:13,270
I'm going to stand before the court

434
00:24:13,270 --> 00:24:14,600
and scold the officials.

435
00:24:14,600 --> 00:24:16,790
If Xu Ningyan is
the Dafeng's conscience,

436
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,990
then I want to be the Dafeng's light,

437
00:24:18,990 --> 00:24:20,200
shining before the court.

438
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,440
Senior Yang, don't.

439
00:24:25,510 --> 00:24:27,840
Holding the sun and moon,
I pluck the stars.

440
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,920
There is no one like me in this world.

441
00:24:33,880 --> 00:24:35,230
Who brought me here?

442
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:37,170
Master, are you going to stop me?

443
00:24:37,470 --> 00:24:38,880
You're being too impatient.

444
00:24:39,070 --> 00:24:41,790
You said I'd be famous once I go back.

445
00:24:42,230 --> 00:24:43,770
Why are you stopping me now?

446
00:24:43,770 --> 00:24:45,310
The capital is full of hidden talents.

447
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:47,120
There's always someone better.

448
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:48,390
Master,

449
00:24:49,200 --> 00:24:50,310
explain clearly.

450
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,070
I mean

451
00:24:52,070 --> 00:24:53,990
you should hide your weaknesses.

452
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:56,150
I have

453
00:24:56,310 --> 00:24:57,200
realized it.

454
00:24:57,200 --> 00:24:58,600
What have you realized?

455
00:24:58,600 --> 00:25:00,990
Master, are you stopping me

456
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:03,310
because you're afraid I'll outshine you?

457
00:25:09,640 --> 00:25:10,600
Old man,

458
00:25:10,600 --> 00:25:12,470
let me out!

459
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:14,640
Old man!

460
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,160
It's my turn.

461
00:25:29,030 --> 00:25:29,960
I've just finished

462
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:31,920
handling a small matter.

463
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,460
Your Highness, please forgive me.

464
00:25:35,030 --> 00:25:36,790
Supervisor, your chess skills

465
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,120
aren't as good as before.

466
00:25:40,440 --> 00:25:41,280
But

467
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:43,360
your ability to judge people

468
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:45,510
is still as sharp as ever.

469
00:25:46,030 --> 00:25:46,990
Xu Qi'an

470
00:25:47,440 --> 00:25:48,880
did solve the case.

471
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,790
He didn't fail you.

472
00:25:51,200 --> 00:25:54,270
First, you let me introduce him
to the Guardians,

473
00:25:54,550 --> 00:25:56,710
and you guided him step by step

474
00:25:56,710 --> 00:25:57,710
to solve the Sangbo Case.

475
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:59,070
But

476
00:25:59,990 --> 00:26:02,440
isn't that a bit too early?

477
00:26:04,120 --> 00:26:05,790
I have no other choice.

478
00:26:06,310 --> 00:26:08,120
The Nine Pass is full of villains.

479
00:26:08,710 --> 00:26:09,960
Only in this way

480
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,680
can he fight

481
00:26:11,880 --> 00:26:13,070
with them.

482
00:26:16,120 --> 00:26:17,640
As you say, Supervisor.

483
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:19,600
But there is one thing.

484
00:26:20,400 --> 00:26:22,070
Unless absolutely necessary,

485
00:26:22,510 --> 00:26:24,510
don't involve Lin'an.

486
00:26:27,750 --> 00:26:29,200
You're right, Your Highness.

487
00:26:29,470 --> 00:26:30,600
I'll remember that.

488
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:43,830
Good move.

489
00:26:46,900 --> 00:26:53,900
(Xu Mansion)

490
00:26:56,030 --> 00:26:56,870
Honey,

491
00:26:57,270 --> 00:27:00,030
have you told Cijiu that we've moved?

492
00:27:00,030 --> 00:27:00,870
Don't worry.

493
00:27:01,070 --> 00:27:02,600
Ningyan is reliable.

494
00:27:02,600 --> 00:27:04,920
He must've written to the Academy.

495
00:27:05,750 --> 00:27:06,920
Welcome.

496
00:27:06,920 --> 00:27:08,310
Congratulations.

497
00:27:08,310 --> 00:27:09,310
You're here.

498
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:11,200
Yes, now your family

499
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,440
has two talents.

500
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,470
From now on,

501
00:27:13,470 --> 00:27:15,880
you'll live a life
of endless wealth and honor.

502
00:27:15,880 --> 00:27:17,540
- No.
- This is a perfect gift

503
00:27:17,540 --> 00:27:18,710
(Nourishing Cream)
for you.

504
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,500
Try this cream.
It's perfect for your skin.

505
00:27:20,500 --> 00:27:22,130
Your skin will be as smooth and bright

506
00:27:22,130 --> 00:27:22,870
as white jade.

507
00:27:22,990 --> 00:27:25,270
Thanks. This is really good.

508
00:27:25,710 --> 00:27:27,510
Wealth and honor are beyond our reach.

509
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,230
We're just getting by.

510
00:27:29,230 --> 00:27:30,160
Getting by?

511
00:27:30,230 --> 00:27:31,550
You call this getting by?

512
00:27:31,550 --> 00:27:33,160
Look at the house you chose.

513
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:34,230
It's quiet yet convenient,

514
00:27:34,230 --> 00:27:35,510
a perfect retreat.

515
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:37,230
Living here must be comfortable.

516
00:27:37,230 --> 00:27:38,270
Come on.

517
00:27:38,270 --> 00:27:39,840
It's quite secluded.

518
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,400
From East City to West City,

519
00:27:42,550 --> 00:27:44,920
the coachman took an hour to find here.

520
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:45,790
I got dizzy

521
00:27:45,790 --> 00:27:47,030
from all the turning.

522
00:27:48,750 --> 00:27:50,600
If you don't feel well,

523
00:27:50,600 --> 00:27:51,790
you should go rest

524
00:27:51,790 --> 00:27:52,920
and eat something.

525
00:27:53,070 --> 00:27:54,680
Never mind. I'm not hungry.

526
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:57,120
I had a bird's nest and snow frog stew
for breakfast.

527
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,310
It hasn't been digested yet.

528
00:27:59,790 --> 00:28:01,030
Don't let her get to you.

529
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:03,790
Her husband used to work
in the Ministry of Rites.

530
00:28:03,790 --> 00:28:05,160
Because of the Sangbo Case,

531
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:07,330
he's still detained
in the Ministry of Justice.

532
00:28:07,360 --> 00:28:09,310
How could she be in the mood
to eat anything?

533
00:28:09,510 --> 00:28:12,120
It's just a routine inquiry.

534
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:13,880
He'll be back in a few days.

535
00:28:13,880 --> 00:28:15,550
Didn't you just tell me

536
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:17,260
that this time he's in trouble,

537
00:28:17,260 --> 00:28:18,790
and you were trying to ask Xu Ningyan

538
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:20,200
to intercede for him?

539
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:22,920
Ridiculous.

540
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:26,120
Xu Ningyan is just a Copper Gong.

541
00:28:26,470 --> 00:28:27,680
He can't possibly

542
00:28:27,840 --> 00:28:29,550
have a say in such a matter.

543
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:31,920
The Guardians are here.

544
00:28:53,700 --> 00:28:55,820
(Xu Mansion)

545
00:29:07,550 --> 00:29:08,750
Mr. Yang, Mr. Nangong.

546
00:29:08,750 --> 00:29:10,990
Sorry for the improper welcome.

547
00:29:12,160 --> 00:29:13,160
Mr. Xu,

548
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:14,610
on behalf of the Guardians,

549
00:29:14,610 --> 00:29:16,880
we're here to congratulate you
on moving to a new house.

550
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:19,470
Thank you.

551
00:29:19,960 --> 00:29:21,440
It's truly an honor

552
00:29:21,440 --> 00:29:23,790
for our family to have you here.

553
00:29:23,790 --> 00:29:25,470
We're truly honored.

554
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:33,840
Where is Lord Wei?

555
00:29:34,270 --> 00:29:35,470
Lord Wei said he'd come.

556
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:37,710
Lord Wei is busy,

557
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,680
so he asked us to come

558
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,510
and congratulate you on his behalf.

559
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:44,750
We understand.

560
00:29:44,840 --> 00:29:45,710
Everyone,

561
00:29:45,710 --> 00:29:46,920
please, come inside.

562
00:29:46,920 --> 00:29:48,400
We still have matters to attend to,

563
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,160
so we won't trouble you further.

564
00:29:54,030 --> 00:29:55,440
- Goodbye.
- Safe travels.

565
00:29:55,440 --> 00:29:57,160
- Congrats, Mr. Xu.
- Thank you.

